articles.title: French anti-graft police search headquarters of Paris 2024 Olympics - FRANCE 24 English
articles.description: Police raided the headquarters of the Paris 2024 Olympics on Tuesday just over a year before the opening ceremony of the quadrennial sporting showpiece.
